CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 5, 1969, pg. 17 reads: "Dee Dee And Sponsor - Singer Dee Dee Warwick (left), star of the show at the Milicka's Cabaret, is shown here with the club's sponsor, Mrs. Ida Jones, Miss Warwick is the sister of singer-actress Dionne Warwick."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of singer Dee Dee Warwick and Ida Jones, standing in Rostraver Gardens for Milickas Civic Club "Do Your Thing" Cabaret, Belle Vernon
